Title: Requires federally qualified health centers and rural health centers cover the cost of all ovulation enhancing drugs dispensed
Summary: Requires federally qualified health centers and rural health centers cover the cost of all ovulation enhancing drugs dispensed and other covered entities pursuant to section 340B of the federal public health service act.
LawCode: Amd ยง2807, Pub Health L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law, in relation to requiring federally qualified health centers and rural health centers cover the cost of all ovulation enhancing drugs dispensed
